de>CSSMediaRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>画面の幅を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>lWidth</var> = window.screen.width\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js; notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Crude way to check that the screen is at least 1024x768</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>width <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1024</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>screen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>height <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;=</span> <span class=\"token number\">768</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Resolution is 1024x768 or above</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"注","isH3":false,"content":"<p>このプロパティによって与えられた幅のすべてがウィンドウ自体に利用できるとは限らないことに注意してください。他のウィジェットが <code>window</code> オブジェクトで使用できない空間を占有している場合は、 <code>window.screen.width</code> と <code>window.screen.availWidth</code> に違いがあります。 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/height\"><code>screen.height</code></a> も参照してください。</p>\n\n<p>Internet Explorer は、画面の幅を報告する際に拡大率の設定を考慮します。拡大率が 100% に設定されている場合のみ、実際の画面の幅を返します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-screen-height\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM) View Module<br><small lang=\"ja\">Screen.height の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">草案</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Screen.height","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Screen/width/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"注","id":"notes"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specification"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"画面の幅を